The ISRI Analytic Tools for OCR Evalutaion

Originally developed by Dr. Steven Rice in 1996 for his doctoral dissertation,
it has been revived by @eddieantonio to continue its OCR evaluation goodness
for all of the languages representable by Unicode — including Haida!

